c: 9
v: 19
t: "Korosey Cajji marat abtan feqyaa (effeqyaa) kee masgidil caramat abtan xisne Yallaa kee ellecaboh ayró nummayseeh Yallih gital yingicilee numih inna abtaanaah missossaanaa? Moominiin kee koros Yallih xaqul mamissowtak, Yalli isi nafsi koroosannut yudlume mara kayri taamal tirri mahaa"